@AccessControl.authorizationCheck: #NOT_REQUIRED
@EndUserText.label: 'NTTDATA Integration Type'
@Metadata.ignorePropagatedAnnotations: true
define root view entity YNDBS_R_INTEGRATION_TYPE
  as select from yndbs_a_int_coc


  association [0..1] to YNDBS_R_DATA_TYPE    as IntegrationDataType    on  IntegrationDataType.Value    = $projection.DataType
                                                                       and IntegrationDataType.language = $session.system_language


  association [0..1] to YNDBS_R_SERVICE_TYPE as IntegrationServiceType on  IntegrationServiceType.ServiceType = $projection.ServiceType



{

  key integration_id                         as IntegrationId,
      integration_name                       as IntegrationName,
      integration_entity                     as IntegrationEntity,
      integration_example_link               as IntegrationExampleLink,
      service_type                           as ServiceType,
      IntegrationServiceType.ServiceTypeName as ServiceTypeName,
      data_type                              as DataType,
      IntegrationDataType.Description        as DataTypeName,
      is_synchronous                         as IsSynchronous
}
